{"tid":650011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地殘障男征高速公路　飛馳32公里始被截 烈火三輪車由福田殺到獅隧","createTime":"2018-05-02T03:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T04:37:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef7e2baaf943d929b6855eadd72eff5b8fe880c","tid":650011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180502/20378688?_ga=2.112889476.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F20378688%3F_ga%3D2.112889476.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=nRHBUVZHhqwhhyqBOnRgtMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=49a95df3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180502%2F20378688%3F_ga%3D2.112889476.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=9d1e4b49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180502/20378688?_ga=2.112889476.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月02日 <br />\n<br />\n內地殘障男征高速公路　飛馳32公里始被截<br />\n烈火三輪車由福田殺到獅隧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180502/large/a0501a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180502%2Flarge%2Fa0501a.gif&h=00d2f72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地男昨在吐露港公路行車線中央駕駛電動三輪車。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】行車時速可達100公里的高速公路竟有迷你電動三輪車飛馳！不良於行的內地男遊客昨趁五一假期經福田口岸入境後，駕駛自攜的電動三輪車，由落馬洲輾轉經吐露港公路，行駛約32公里至獅子山隧道口始被截停，警方事後將他連同電動三輪車一併帶走調查，警方最終口頭警告了事。內地客辯稱不知道在港駕駛電動三輪車可能違法。<br />\n<br />\n記者：姜偉康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉事的內地遊客姓高，29歲，河北人，他昨向記者表示他因病致右腳不良於行，半年前在深圳經淘寶網買了一部可摺叠、時速達30公里的電動三輪車代步，他聲稱獲內地發出證明傷殘證件，平日在深圳馬路駕駛該部電動車並無問題。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180502/large/a0501b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180502%2Flarge%2Fa0501b.gif&h=8e5df0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員不拘控僅警告<br />\n<br />\n昨晨10時許，事主趁五一假期來旅遊，他帶着該部電動三輪車經福田口岸來港，目的地是灣仔金紫荊廣場及中環等觀光地點。他表示，由福田入境香港時，海關讓他使用傷殘人士的特別通道過關，但入境後他準備乘搭港鐵時，卻被落馬洲支線的港鐵職員拒諸閘外，不容他攜電動車乘列車，他惟有使用手機的地圖引路，駕駛其電動車沿粉嶺公路及吐露港公路南下。<br />\n<br />\n昨日中午12時左右，他駕駛三輪車行經吐露港公路時，被其他駕駛人士發覺並被拍下其驚險情況，照片隨即在fb熱傳。事主駕車20多公里後終在沙田區停下遊覽及吃午飯，並獲好心餐廳職員為他的三輪車充電。<br />\n<br />\n下午4時許充滿電後，他再啟程準備經獅子山隧道出九龍，但到達隧道口收費亭時即被隧道公司職員截停及報警，警方到場調查後將他連人帶車帶返警署調查，結束他在港約32公里的奇妙之旅。事主聲稱不知道沒牌照在港公路駕駛電動三輪車有可能違法，警方調查後認為高駕駛的只是電動三輪輪椅，只口頭警告了事，沒作拘控。<br />\n<br />\n據淘寶網，與事主駕駛的電動三輪車同牌子產品，售價約3,500至4,000元人民幣，時速達35公里，充滿電最遠可行駛40公里。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n深圳撿12.5億元可卡因拘9港人<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n大狀：或涉3宗罪"},{"pid":"e31a72b8ad2f30ed93abb7dd24a5f9479b7d6f32","tid":650011,"uid":59358,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"警方最終口頭警告了事 ...... <br />\n好撚嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ccc6f7e2905bbe5b76f3bb46b3ce27567ab06b","tid":650011,"uid":31927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:26:17.000Z","msg":"電動三輪輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW 有時D傷殘人仕電動輪椅係行人路開得好撚快"},{"pid":"1e8a94ca1e35d1fd50f44e54d8d32d98c456aaa0","tid":650011,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:34:55.000Z","msg":"充滿電先最多行個零鐘..."},{"pid":"9a3dffb9b09546aef6f4f7debb8cb32312f13413","tid":650011,"uid":171058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"黑警就係咁L樣!"},{"pid":"16501d0b9fd490f0087ec615141dedd55aed0a1f","tid":650011,"uid":48234,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"支那狗犯法與港人同罪呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"17ece6219f235ebdf67ba6bff887615b15408d6c","tid":650011,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e344c76ae1820821e65ff660a1b0bf588a97b4e5","tid":650011,"uid":49588,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"中國人在香港犯法，是不會比起訴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fb34a26006dc315f3d1589954ff05119151e0e","tid":650011,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87837de63b3fdf412e31789469455d87bcd01705","tid":650011,"uid":26937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國人在香港犯法，是不會比起訴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真的<br />\n只會叫佢返上去<br />\n告佢唔入"},{"pid":"779cb6a1dc86f5a0e27fdae6f6a80784d4923ec3","tid":650011,"uid":53466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7ae3c8800961a6d1adfc3587690381a16d2cc85","tid":650011,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"一句我是支那來的就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305d002034ce7ba19b1f25d77bb0d67216333245","tid":650011,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"有速度 儲電量大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d6150d481ba2e68365ef51182ba6ae75718752","tid":650011,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-